{"name": "001 Self-Portrait 1", "description": "Nounscapes is a tribute to Nouns, their artists, and the pixel aesthetic that shaped my sensibilities at a young age.

The central idea of Nounscapes is to bend and repurpose Noun traits into something other than they were initially meant for. Sometimes they create a scene, tell a story, or invoke symbolism.

All mint proceeds are recycled and, eventually, fed back into Nouns DAO via auction bids. So the beautiful wheel can keep turning.

Provenounce is key,
